ou3

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • ou3.Node

  • public class Node
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class of the Node, existing at a position in the Network. Will keep track off the nearby Node s to which Message s can be sent, The list of Event s that has happened at the Node, and a routingTable of information concerning how to get to other Event s. Must also know if able to recieve or send a Message this round.
    See Also:
    Network
